premise_source_doc_sentence: CeeLo Green 's The Good Life is an American comedy series created and hosted by CeeLo Green .

Thomas DeCarlo Callaway  (  born May 30 , 1974 , better known by his stage name CeeLo Green  (  sometimes rendered as Cee Lo Green  )  , is an American singer , rapper , songwriter , record producer , actor , and businessman .
